 1. Specify the environment variables and values in your service manifests. If you already have environment variables specified you probably already have these.

```
&lt;CodePackage Name=&quot;MyCode&quot; Version=&quot;CodeVersion1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;EnvironmentVariables&gt;
              &lt;EnvironmentVariable Name=&quot;MyEnvVariable&quot; Value=&quot;DefaultValue&quot;/&gt;
              &lt;EnvironmentVariable Name=&quot;HttpGatewayPort&quot; Value=&quot;19080&quot;/&gt;
        &lt;/EnvironmentVariables&gt;
&lt;/CodePackage&gt;
```
 2. Add the environment variable overrides in the application manifest

```
&lt;ServiceManifestImport&gt;
    &lt;ServiceManifestVersion=&quot;1.0.0&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;EnvironmentOverrides CodePackageRef=&quot;MyCode&quot;&gt;
      &lt;EnvironmentVariable Name=&quot;MyEnvVariable&quot; Value=&quot;OverrideValue&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/EnvironmentOverrides&gt;
  &lt;/ServiceManifestImport&gt;
```

 3. In the application manifest, instead of a specific overridden value, specify the environment variable value as an application parameter.

```
&lt;ServiceManifestImport&gt;
    &lt;ServiceManifestVersion=&quot;1.0.0&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;EnvironmentOverrides CodePackageRef=&quot;MyCode&quot;&gt;
      &lt;EnvironmentVariable Name=&quot;MyEnvVariable&quot; Value=&quot;[MyEnvVariableOverride]&quot;/&gt;
    &lt;/EnvironmentOverrides&gt;
  &lt;/ServiceManifestImport&gt;

```
and

```
&lt;Parameters&gt;
   &lt;Parameter Name=&quot;MyEnvVariableOverride&quot; DefaultValue=&quot;DefaultOverrideValue&quot; /&gt;
&lt;/Parameters&gt;

```

 4. Do an application upgrade that changes the application parameters via the `ApplicationParameters` hashtable (in PS - mapping of parameter name to parameter value). For example you would set &quot;MyEnvVariableOverride&quot; to &quot;FinalValue&quot;. This will flow down and cause the environment variable value that the service sees to change. Note that changing environment variables requires that the process restart.

Relevant docs: [1], [2], [3], [4]

[1]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/service-fabric/service-fabric-how-to-specify-environment-variables#procedure-for-specifying-environment-variables-for-services
[2]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/service-fabric/service-fabric-how-to-parameterize-configuration-files
[3]: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/service-fabric/service-fabric-application-upgrade-parameters
[4]: https://github.com/Azure-Samples/service-fabric-dotnet-data-aggregation#application-parameter-upgrade

